Routine Descriptions

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_BURST1_V01

 [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 burst1 data (E and B fields) v01 cdfs.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_burst1_v01.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_ESVY_DESPUN_V03

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 esvy_despun v03 cdfs.
   v01 and v02 files are not in the same format. v03 cdfs will be in the same format.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_esvy_despun_v03.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_ESVY_DESPUN_V04

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 esvy_despun v04 cdfs.

 v03 time tags are off by 1/32 sec. This is fixed in v04.

 Note the time tags are fixed at rbsp_efw_phasef_read_e_uvw---a lower
   level program. Thus the codes for generating v04 data are the same as v03.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_esvy_despun_v04.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_E_HIRES_UVW_V02

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 e_hires_uvw v02 cdfs.
   v01 files are not in the same format. v02 cdfs will be in the same format.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_e_hires_uvw_v02.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_E_HIRES_UVW_V03

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 e_hires_uvw v03 cdfs.
   v02 time tag is off by 1/32 sec. This is corrected in v03.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_e_hires_uvw_v03.pro)

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 e_spinfit v04 cdfs.

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines]

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_fbk_v02.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_SPEC_V02

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 spec v02 cdfs.
   v01 files are not in the same format. v02 cdfs will be in the same format.
 Needs to save v01 files in a folder spec_v01, which is two levels up the file hierachy from the v02 file.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_spec_v02.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_VSVY_HIRES_V03

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 vsvy_hires v03 cdfs.
   v03 files will be in the same format.
   v03 uses the spice orbit_num (v02 uses ect orbit_num, which is sometimes wrong)

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_vsvy_hires_v03.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_GEN_L2_VSVY_HIRES_V04

 [Previous Routine] [Next Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Generate L2 vsvy_hires v04 cdfs.
   v03 time tags are off by 1/32 sec. This is fixed in v04.
   v03 -A uses -B's skeleton. This is fixed in v04.

 Note the time tags are fixed at rbsp_efw_phasef_read_vsvy---a lower
   level program. Thus the codes for generating v04 data are the same as v03.

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_gen_l2_vsvy_hires_v04.pro)

RBSP_EFW_PHASEF_READ_L2

 [Previous Routine] [List of Routines] 
 Read EFW L2 data.

 datatype can be 'e-hires-uvw','e-spinfit-mgse','esvy_despun','fbk','spec','vsvy-hires'

(See general/missions/rbsp/efw/rbsp_phasef/file_production/l2/rbsp_efw_phasef_read_l2.pro)
